00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:23,120
He has taken refuge at the Japanese Embassy in Dongjiaominxiang.

159
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:28,480
Sun Yat-sen issued the "Declaration of Rebellion" in Shanghai,

160
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,808
[Chen Duxiu, styled Zhongfu, Dean of Liberal Arts at Peking University]

161
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:31,200
