There are also some students

174
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,480
who spontaneously, in the early morning,

175
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,720
went to the streets to raise awareness and rouse the people.

176
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,880
There are also a few on campus

177
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,080
who support the restoration,

178
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,280
such as Gu Hongming,

179
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,760
who is said to be appointed

180
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:10,640
Vice Minister of Foreign Affairs of the Qing court.

181
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,600
What about that Liu Shipei?

182
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,200
I haven't heard yet.

183
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,400
Sir, we have an urgent message to tell you.

184
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,520
That's fine, say it here.

185
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,720
We're all comrades here.

186
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,400
At the school gate, the Queue Army's cavalry

187
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:22,000
claimed to have arrested rebels against the imperial court.

188
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,120
Who are they taking?

189
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,200
On the list is Guo Xingang, a liberal arts student,

190
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,400
Deng Zhongxia, and so on.

191
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,280
