192
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,040
Outrageous.

193
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,560
Inform the doorman to close the school gate.

194
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,280
We cannot let the Queue Army's cavalry rush into the campus.

195
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,520
You get my car ready.

196
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,480
Yes.

197
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,240
Master Cai, don't get excited.

198
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,560
I am certain this Zhang Xun Restoration

199
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,240
will be a farce

200
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,280
and will not achieve anything.

201
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,800
It would be better to bide our time.

202
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:47,760
Zhongfu. Now, Peking University has become

203
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,120
the benchmark of New Culture.

204
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,120
