210
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:09,920
Zhongfu. Politics can make a big difference.

211
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:13,040
Since the Queue Army is destined to be short-lived,

212
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,280
