233
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,600
Alright.

234
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,320
I told you that you wouldn't let yourself fall behind.

235
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,320
Come to Peking University to teach.

236
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,120
The New Culture Movement advocated by Peking University

237
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:20,240
