238
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,320
I listen to Master Cai.

239
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,960
Just go back.

240
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:28,400
Don't stay here too long now that your position is clear.

241
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,360
