251
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,640
Show him in.

252
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:23,840
You see.

253
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,800
President Cai. Please.

254
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,080
You.

255
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,480
What's so funny?

256
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,320
Why are you laughing?

257
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,920
With the current situation like this,

258
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,040
