278
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,680
which led to the wolf entering the room.

279
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,800
Zhang Xun was encouraged by Duan Qirui

280
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,520
to let Li Yuantong resign and let little Xuantong restore the throne.

281
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:48,160
The result is widespread indignation and discontent, that will be defamed throughout history.

282
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,440
Brother Botang, what do you think?

283
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:56,160
How will this situation develop now?

284
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,200
Now the whole country is denouncing Zhang Xun.

285
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,960
In Tianjin, Duan Qirui

286
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:03,680
has issued a campaign against rebellion.

287
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,120
And organized a rebel army

288
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,720
to attack the capital.

289
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:10,560
Zhang Xun's five-thousand-strong Queue Army

290
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,400
will collapse at the first blow for sure!

291
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:15,520
In the end, Duan Qirui will definitely make a comeback.

292
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:18,080
He defeated Zhang Xun

293
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,840
and drove out Li Yuanhong

294
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,560
and gained a reputation for defending the Republic.

295
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,880
This... This is killing three birds with one stone.

296
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,800
If that's the case,

297
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:30,000
then where does that leave us?

298
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,240
I and Jingsheng can quietly

299
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,000
watch how the current situation will evolve.

300
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,200
And you?

301
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,280
You must leave Beijing as soon as possible.

302
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,720
Lie low.

303
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,051
Why?

304
00:12:40,175 --> 00:12:40,969
Why?

305
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,520
Why must I leave and lie low?

306
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:46,480
Peking University is the first of the new ideological trend.

307
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,000
Once the war starts,

308
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,320
the Queue Clique must be prevented from desperate recklessness

309
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,600
that would make an example out of Peking University.

310
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:52,800
If you ran away,

311
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:55,040
Then you'll have nothing to do with Peking University and Zhang Xun.

312
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:59,920
In the future, it will be a bargaining chip for you with Duan Qirui.

313
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:09,360
Smart, extremely smart.

314
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:12,080
Okay, okay, I'll listen to you.

315
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,920
I'll go back to the school and make arrangements.

316
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:14,960
How about this.

317
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:18,400
I'm going to Tianjin to hide tonight.

318
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,360
Good.

319
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:21,520
That will do, Brother Jiemin.

320
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:23,120
You brought your props

321
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,040
for a spin around my Ministry of Education.

322
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:26,800
You've got a good hand.

323
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:30,000
And even more tricks up your sleeves than him.

324
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:31,840
Come.

325
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,880
I hope this farce will end soon

326
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,280
so that you and I can have peace of mind.

327
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:57,806
Zhongfu!

328
00:13:58,529 --> 00:13:59,514
Zhongfu!

329
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,120
Junman, don't be afraid.

330
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,080
Did you hear it?

331
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,440
What's going on? What was...

332
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,040
What happened?

333
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:14,880
It seems that Duan Qirui's rebel army

334
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,800
is fighting Zhang Xun's Queue Army,

335
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,640
which is far from us.

336
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,720
Will they fire cannons?

337
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,760
They won't.

338
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,600
Neither Duan Qirui nor Zhang Xun dared

339
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,040
to open fire at Beijing.

340
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,320
Don't worry. It's nothing.

341
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,400
You said they wouldn't fire cannons.

342
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,520
What is this?

343
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:36,000
It may be that the rebel army is bombing the city gate with explosives.

344
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,400
Why are you so sure it wasn't cannons?

345
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:40,240
I made explosives with Cai Jiemin.

346
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,600
That's the sound.

347
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,760
Do you think the battle will get to Shanghai?

348
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,280
Will Yannian and Qiaonian be all right?

349
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,120
The battle won't get to Shanghai.

350
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,680
It'll be a few chaotic days at most.

351
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,200
Rest assured.

352
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,040
I have asked someone to bring a message to Wang Mengzou.

353
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:57,600
asking him to take care of Yannian and Qiaonian.

354
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:01,200
Dad, I'm scared!

355
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,000
Don't be scared.

356
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:36,080
Let us through.

357
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:03,680
Take care, sir.

358
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:05,200
Thanks.

359
