00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:57,367
Down with Zhang Xun! Defend the Republic!

375
00:16:57,684 --> 00:16:59,875
Down with Zhang Xun! Defend the Republic!

376
00:17:00,033 --> 00:17:02,235
Down with Zhang Xun! Defend the Republic!

377
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,280
Down with Zhang Xun!

378
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,720
Take a look at "New Youth" magazine.

379
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,720
[Chen Qiaonian, Chen Duxiu's second son]

380
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,280
The Manchu Restoration has made the current political situation unpeaceful.

381
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:08,560
Look!

382
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:10,640
Long queues, short queues.

383
