Real queues, fake queues.

384
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,960
We want to live an ordinary life,

385
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:21,040
you must bring benefit to the common people.

386
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,880
"New Youth", youth is new,

387
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,960
if you want to bring peace to the land

388
