Old men eat my pear-syrup candy.

414
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:18,880
Eat the candy I bought for you.

415
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,000
Thank you, jiejie.

416
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:22,880
Little kids eat my pear-syrup candy,

417
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:26,000
smarty-pants going to school.

418
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,760
Brother, why do you think this Zhang Xun

419
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:29,040
had to do this restoration thing?

420
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,640
Now we can't go to school,

421
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,760
all the shops have closed their doors,

422
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,120
and no one is buying our magazine.

423
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,800
Exactly. My mom wouldn't even let me out.

424
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:36,560
She said the streets are in turmoil.

425
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:38,480
When do you think the chaos will end?

426
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:40,880
Our country is really plagued with misfortune.

427
00:18:41,360 --> 00:18:42,480
The Republic is not even six years old,

428
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:43,920
and there has already been two restorations.

429
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:46,480
What do you think is the cause of this?

430
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,800
I really want to find a knowledgeable person and ask why.

431
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:51,040
What is China's way out?

432
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:52,800
Yannian.

433
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:54,560
Finally found you guys.

434
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,240
Fourth Uncle. Hello Fourth Uncle.

435
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,360
Even with the streets in such chaos,

436
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:00,640
you've still set up your stall?

437
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:01,840
How can we help you?

438
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:03,840
Director Wang told me to look for you two.

439
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,280
There is a guest here from Beijing

440
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,480
who has asked the two of you to eat with them.

441
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,440
A guest here?

442
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:08,160
That's right.

443
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,680
Do you know the name of this guest?

444
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,680
Li Dazhao.

445
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,760
Qiaonian.

446
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,840
Let me see, let me see.

447
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:20,800
So tall!

448
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:24,320
Mr. Wang, I've long heard

449
00:19:23,749 --> 00:19:25,320
[Wang Mengzou, Manager of Yadong Library]

450
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:26,160
that brother Zhongfu's two sons are great.

451
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,560
Honest to a fault, chivalrous and daring.

452
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:31,200
Seeing you two today, you are indeed heroic youth

453
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:32,400
with exceptional bearing.

454
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,600
Mr. Shouchang,

455
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:35,760
Qiaonian and I are your admirers.

456
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,920
We can both recite your essay "Youth" from memory.

457
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:39,360
That makes me very happy.

458
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,360
That essay was written for youth

459
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,240
like the two of you.

460
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:43,360
Come, sit.

461
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:45,440
Mr. Shouchang, let's move to the drawing room.

462
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,720
No need. It's fine here.

463
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:47,680
Then sit here, please.

464
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,440
It's no bother, Mr. Wang.

465
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:50,320
Sit here.

466
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,160
I'm ashamed to be here this time.

467
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,640
Running off in a panic, in dire straits.

468
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:56,800
Brother Zhongfu brought word

469
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,880
that I must come to the Yadong Library.

470
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:01,360
First, to let everyone know we are safe.

471
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:04,080
Second, to investigate "New Youth"'s

472
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:04,720
operational condition.

473
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,880
Third, to make some new friends.

474
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:08,400
I'm sorry to have inconvenienced you.

475
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,520
Not at all, not at all.

476
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:12,560
How is Zhongfu?

477
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:15,040
Your father is very busy person right now.

478
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:17,440
He is helping Mr. Cai with reforms at Peking University,

479
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,360
which are going swimmingly.

480
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,040
Running "New Youth",

481
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,480
advocating for the New Culture movement,

482
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,480
it's all very impressive.

483
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,720
It's only that the current political situation is difficult.

484
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,880
Every step forward is challenging.

485
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:31,680
To be able to move a bit every day, like a pawn, is productive enough.

486
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,080
Mr. Shouchang,

487
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:35,920
does this Zhang Xun Restoration

488
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:38,160
affect the reforms at Peking University?

489
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,320
The new zeitgeist of reform at Peking University

490
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:42,720
is definitely intolerable for the likes of Zhang Xun.

491
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:44,800
But at the moment it looks like

492
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:47,040
the restoration will come to a premature end.

493
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,800
As for the situation in the future,

494
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,160
it depends.

495
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:54,000
Then what do you think about the present state of affairs?

496
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:57,120
I think the situation is not encouraging.

497
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:59,360
Brother Zhongfu once said

498
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,520
that after Yuan Shikai

499
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,880
there is bound to be a period of fighting between warlords.

500
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:06,720
And now everyone can see.

501
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,320
Europe has gone to war.

502
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,080
The world is a mess.

503
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,560
China is poor and weak.

504
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,320
Fragmented and disorganized like a heap of sand.

505
00:21:14,560 --> 00:21:17,680
With internal trouble and external aggression, it is hard to be independent.

506
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,880
If China is like this, what is the way forward?

507
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:22,640
The Zhang Xun Restoration

508
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:24,560
broke the hearts of many people.

509
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,720
No hint in sight for which course to follow

510
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:28,880
to get out of the predicament.

511
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:30,720
But none of us have given up.

512
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,080
Then from what you can tell,

513
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,360
do you think the theory of anarchism

514
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,120
can help China?

515
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:39,040
I don't think so.

516
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,440
I've read anarchist books.

517
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,680
This theory seems to hold a lot of attraction.

518
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,120
But very utopian.

519
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,880
I'm afraid it won't work in practice.

520
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:49,600
I think Kropotkin's Mutual Aid

521
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,040
can solve China's problems.

522
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,640
Moreover, it is the only way out.

523
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:56,080
Yannian,

524
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:58,080
do you see a single country in Europe

525
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:01,200
forming its state policy in accordance with the doctrine of mutual aid?

526
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:03,760
You're still young now.

527
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,520
At this time,

528
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:08,160
there is no harm in reading widely, listeningly widely.

529
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:11,600
In considering problems and thinking things through, don't go to the extremes.

530
00:22:14,320 --> 00:22:16,160
Mr. Shouchang is right.

531
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:21,120
Do you have any plans for this visit to Shanghai?

532
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:23,280
I plan to use this time

533
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:25,440
to properly sort out my own thoughts

534
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:27,120
and reflect on some questions.

535
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:29,680
I also want to spend some time amongst the people.

536
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:32,240
I want to see the real China,

537
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,240
what it's actually like.

538
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,280
Mr. Li.

539
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,240
Hello.

540
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:37,520
Mengzou,

541
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:40,000
the table has been set, and the wine has been warmed.

