As long as you can come to Peking University to teach, then it's fine.

811
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,000
You see, it can work.

812
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:27,200
Master Cai, just arrange for me to take orders.

813
00:34:28,240 --> 00:34:29,120
How is it?

814
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:33,120
Yucai comes over to Peking University to become a liberal arts professor.

815
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:35,040
You, as the Dean of Liberal Arts

816
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,960
must immediately arrange his course well.

817
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:38,080
Excellent!

818
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,080
Another key figure is added to Peking University.

819
00:34:40,560 --> 00:34:42,640
You should say our New Culture Movement

820
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:44,640
has added another key figure.

821
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:47,920
I describe the pen in Yucai's hands

822
00:34:48,160 --> 00:34:50,080
like a surgeon's scalpel.

823
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,160
Incomparably sharp.

824
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:53,680
Yes. Our "New Youth"

825
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,920
was looking forward to Brother Yucai's writings early on.

826
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:58,480
I still hope Brother Yucai can draft many more.

827
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,880
Give what drafts?

828
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,880
Come to "New Youth".

829
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,160
Be a fellow editor.

830
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:06,960
If New Culture doesn't have a vanguard like you,

831
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:09,120
then that is a very big flaw.

832
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,720
How about it?

833
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:15,120
Yucai, the words that Mr. Zhongfu said just now

834
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:16,320
is the real thing.

835
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:19,600
Every word I say is to wish you can come to Peking University.

836
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:21,840
How is it? Become a member.

837
00:35:23,680 --> 00:35:24,640
I'll listen to Master Cai.

838
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:27,520
Good! Brother Yucai.

839
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:30,720
You can join "New Youth".

840
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:32,400
Extremely honored.

841
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,040
Excellent.

842
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:36,320
Today is really a good day.

843
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,320
Shizhi (=Hu Shi), Yucai have all come.

844
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:42,000
Master Cai, then I will prepare to go to Shanghai now.

845
00:35:42,240 --> 00:35:42,800
You hurry and go.

846
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:44,720
Yucai, wait for me until I come back from Shanghai

847
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,680
to come to my house.

848
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,960
"New Youth" is at my house.

849
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,280
See you later, see you later!

850
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,400
Safe travels!

851
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,640
Yucai.

852
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,960
Zhongfu is a carefree person.

853
00:35:57,520 --> 00:35:58,560
Free and unconstrained.

854
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:00,080
Don't take offense.

855
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,280
Come, please sit.

856
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:04,480
The second matter I want to ask you to do

857
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:07,840
is to design a university crest for Peking University.

858
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,040
University crest?

859
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:11,680
Okay.

860
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:14,320
Then do you have any specific opinions and requirements.

861
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,560
I don't have specific requirements.

862
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:18,880
Yucai, your opinions

863
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,240
is my, Cai Yuanpei's opinion.

864
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,080
Master Cai, you have spoken highly of me.

865
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:25,120
No, I have never flattered people.

866
00:36:25,680 --> 00:36:27,440
I think the most acute and profound problems

867
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:30,080
are seen in China at present.

868
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:32,400
You, Zhou Shuren are one who has seen them.

869
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:35,040
I believe the crest you will design for Peking University,

870
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,800
the students of Peking University

871
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:39,200
will continue to wear it for generations to come.

872
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,280
It will never fade.

873
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:48,720
Okay. I'll try.

874
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,720
Younger brother! Let me have a bite!

875
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:55,840
Not giving it to you!

876
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,040
Let me have a bite!

877
00:36:57,520 --> 00:36:58,560
Zimei, don't fight over that with Henian

878
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,600
Mom's frying over here.

879
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:05,360
Mom! Fry one for me.

880
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:06,560
Aren't I frying here?

881
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:07,840
It'll be done right away. Don't be anxious.

882
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,680
Henian! Give me a bite!

883
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,680
Junman!

884
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:12,800
You've come back!

885
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,240
Help me pack my luggage. I am going to Shanghai.

886
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:14,880
Going to Shanghai?

887
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,360
Right.

888
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:16,320
When are you going?

889
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,280
Early tomorrow morning.

890
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:19,760
Then I'll hurry over to walk around Qianmen Street.

891
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,280
What are you going to Qianmen Street for?

892
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,880
To buy Qiaonian and Yannian some things.

893
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:25,360
I am going there to receive Hu Shi, Hu Shizhi.

894
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,520
Then, you're not going to see the two boys at Shanghai?

895
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:30,000
Then when I bump into them, I'll meet them.

896
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:32,640
So, bumping into them means should still buy some things.

897
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:34,640
Come, come here and fry something for the two.

898
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,080
I'll hurry up and go.

899
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:37,680
Don't buy too much, okay?

900
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:39,200
I only have one suitcase, not bringing much.

901
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,400
Alright, just one luggage.

902
00:37:43,129 --> 00:37:49,065
[Shanghai]

903
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:52,640
Zhongfu, why did take so many bags?

904
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,800
Big bags, small bundles, are you escaping from a famine?

905
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:55,920
Gao Junman!

906
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,200
I already said I'm only bringing one bag.

907
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:58,880
All of a sudden, she managed to pack five!

908
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:00,400
Just for the two punks

909
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:01,840
to have food, clothes, drinks and tools!

910
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,920
She's almost moved the whole Qianmen pavilion over.

911
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:07,680
Junman is also very good to the children.

912
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:09,600
This... this suitcase.

913
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,760
There's still give more bags.

914
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:12,960
It seems there's eight bags.

915
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:15,120
Anyways, there's already this many, and I'm not lacking those few.

916
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,400
I'll add another three bags.

917
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,600
Where's Hu Shi?

918
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,736
He went back home.

919
00:38:20,892 --> 00:38:21,778
He went back home?

920
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:24,080
It's like this. His mother has gotten ill all of a sudden.

921
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:26,160
Yesterday morning a telegram arrived

922
00:38:26,560 --> 00:38:27,760
in the afternoon he hurried back.

923
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:29,520
He had me tell you

924
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,560
wait for him to finish handling his family maters, then he'll go to Beijing to hold the teaching position.

925
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:33,680
As a matter of fact, yesterday

926
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,960
I still wanted to give you a telegram.

927
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,480
You were already on the road, though.

928
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:40,240
Where are Qiaonian, Yannian?

929
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:41,280
At Aurora University.

930
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,800
Then I'm going to Jixi, to look for Shizhi.

931
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,640
What are you going to Jixi for?

932
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:46,080
Someone went back home to handle private matters.

933
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,680
If you go, won't you give people an inconvenience?

934
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,680
How about this. You help me take these bags

935
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:50,800
to go to Aurora University

936
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,320
and give these things over to Yannian and Qiaonian.

937
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:53,680
Otherwise these things will go bad.

938
00:38:54,080 --> 00:38:54,800
D-d-don't go.

939
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,080
You also don't need to go to the school.

940
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:57,600
I'll talk to the two

941
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,120
and get them to come see you.

942
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,320
Then what did I come here for?

943
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:03,120
Don't be so anxious, listen to me.

944
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:06,240
There's two friends, they heard you came to Shanghai.

945
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:07,840
Wants to urgently come see you.

946
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:08,480
Who?

947
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:11,200
Yi Baisha, Zou Yongcheng.

948
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:12,880
They're in Shanghai?

949
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:13,360
They are in Shanghai.

950
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:15,360
Brother Zhongfu!

951
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,560
Yongcheng!

952
00:39:18,240 --> 00:39:21,840
Zhongfu.

953
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,360
I missed you, Zhongfu.

954
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,240
Is everything alright you guys?

955
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,160
Hurry and sit.

956
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,080
Here.

957
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,600
You guys... how did you guys get together?

958
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:46,160
Zhongfu.

959
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,800
My unit got dissolved.

960
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,680
[Zou Yongcheng, styled Qizhi]

961
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,760
Right now I'm in the provincial military governor's office, working as an advisor.

962
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:54,800
Honestly, there's really nothing to do.

963
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:57,120
As a matter of fact, Baisha was at Hunan teaching.

964
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,280
Us two often group up to drink our sorrows away.

965
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:00,611
[Yi Baisha, styled Yuecun, Scholar of the New Culture Movement]

966
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:02,480
Coming back this time, is to procure arms for the Hunan army.

967
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,480
He is my advisor.

968
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:07,200
Baisha, you, this master,

969
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,400
why are you also playing with firearms?

970
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,000
Why can't I be playing with firearms?

971
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,320
You also once followed Mr. Cai Yuanpei.

972
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:13,520
Didn't you make a bomb?

973
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:16,000
Baisha.

974
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:18,240
Is there a matter you are not happy with?

975
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:22,240
He went to Guangzhou and saw Mr. [Sun] Yat-sen who returned.

976
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:25,280
What did Mr. [Sun] Yat-sen say to you?

977
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:26,960
Warlords.

978
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:29,760
Defeat the warlords.

979
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:34,400
Defeat the warlords. Easier said than done.

980
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:36,480
How many warlords are there in China?

981
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,840
Which warlord

982
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,520
does not have a foreign power behind him?

983
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:41,600
Fortunately, Europe at war.

984
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,680
Otherwise,

985
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,040
they would've divided China up early on.

986
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,440
Lamentable, so lamentable.

987
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,440
Such a big country like this

988
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:53,120
unexpectedly we don't have a unifying leader.

989
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,600
These warlords, each and every one,

990
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:58,000
has an ugly appearance of "as soon as you finish singing, I go on stage".

991
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:00,720
Creating a foul atmosphere and causing everything to be in disarray.

992
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,080
Leaving people bitterly disappointed.

993
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:03,840
In the eyes of these warlords

994
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:07,760
Mr. [Sun] Yat-sen is actually just a figurehead.

995
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,640
The founder of the Republic.

996
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,480
The leader of the revolutionaries.

997
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,800
Recognized around the world.

998
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:18,640
The Chinese people's key figure

999
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:25,120
right now in each and every warlord

1000
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:27,280
is being played with in the palm of their hands.

1001
00:41:27,517 --> 00:41:28,973
Suffering time and time again.

1002
00:41:30,720 --> 00:41:32,960
This country is finished.
